data.description: Come live in a vacation spot! People pay a lot of money to spend time in a place like this...but you can live here! Your own pond that's really more like a small lake...it has a fountain that lights up at night! Set back off the road, so there's plenty of privacy...surrounded on 3 sides by a retreat camp...woods cover it all so really no neighbors. 2 car garage with additional space for a workshop or office. Inside there's a lovely living room that flows through to the dining room and is open to the kitchen. In addition to the 3 main floor bedrooms, there's a loft that lends itself to multiple uses.
